<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <% include ../partials/meta %>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="keywords" content="" >
    <meta name="description" content="" >
    <% include ../partials/css %>
    <% include ../partials/tongji %>
</head>
<body class="user-page user-cart-page">

<% include ../partials/header-sub %>

<% if(items.length) { %>
<h4><i class="am-icon-check-circle"></i> 购物车目前共有<strong>2</strong>件商品,总价值约为<strong>¥998</strong>,请依次点击每件商品的"加入到淘宝购物车"进行选购:</h4>
<%}%>

<% if(items.length) { %>
    <ul class="main-list">
    <% for(var i=0; i< items.length;i++) {%>
    <li>
        <div class="img">
            <%if (items[i].get('isHot')){ %><em class="hot"></em><%}%>
            <%if (items[i].get('isNewSale')){ %><em class="new"></em><%}%>
            <a href="/product/detail/<%=items[i].get('productId') %>"><img src="//ac-JoaBcRTt.clouddn.com/3a994354f637e827ae7e.png" class="lazy" width="100" height="100" data-original="<% for(var n in items[i].get('mainImage')) { %><% if(items[i].attributes.mainImage[n].isMainImage) { %><%= items[i].attributes.mainImage[n].url %>?imageMogr2/thumbnail/200<%break;}}%>" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="detail">
            <h3>
                <a href="/product/detail/<%=items[i].get('productId') %>" <%if(items[i].get('isShortStock')) {%>class="out-stock"<%}%> >
                <% if (items[i].get('stock') > 0) { %>[现货]<% } %>
                <% if (items[i].get('isShortStock')) {%>[缺货]<%}%>
                <%= items[i].get('name') %>
                </a>
            </h3>
            <p>
                参考价格: <span class="price">¥<strong> <%= (items[i].get('price') ? items[i].get('price') + '.00' : '-') %></strong></span>
            </p>
            <p>
                <i class="icon-taobao"></i> <a class="shop-add-link" href="<%= items[i].get('shopLink')[0] %>"> 加入到淘宝店铺购物车 <i class="am-icon-check-circle"></i></a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </li>

    <% } %>
</ul>
<% } else { %>
<div class="cart-empty-info">
    <div></div>
    <p>您的购物车暂时还没有任何商品哦! <a href="/">立即去购物</a></p>
</div>
<%}%>


<div class="am-container">
    <% if(items.length) { %>
    <div class="clear-cart-button">
        <button type="button" id="clear-cart" class="am-btn am-btn-default">清空购物车</button>
    </div>
    <%}%>
    <ul class="info">
        <li><i class="am-icon-credit-card color-main"></i> 由于支付权限原因,目前我们仅支持下单后跳转到淘宝店铺进行支付,您可根据系统提示进行后续操作,感谢您的支持和理解!</li>
        <li><i class="am-icon-info-circle color-main"></i> 目前网站价格仅为参考价格,最终价格请结合淘宝店铺零售价为准.</li>
        <li><i class="am-icon-info-circle color-main"></i> 如发生产品对应链接错误,您可以直接在淘宝店铺中搜索该产品名称即可找到对应产品.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="am-modal am-modal-confirm" tabindex="-1" id="modal-clear-cart">
    <div class="am-modal-dialog">
        <div class="am-modal-bd">
            确定要清除购物车么？
        </div>
        <div class="am-modal-footer">
            <span class="am-modal-btn" data-am-modal-cancel>取消</span>
            <span class="am-modal-btn" data-am-modal-confirm>确定</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<% include ../partials/js %>

<script>
    $(function() {
        var cart = require('cart');
        cart.init();
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>